<h1>What is link building?</h1>                                                                                                                  

<p class="glossary-intro"><dfn>Link building</dfn> is a discipline in which marketers attempt to obtain <a href="https://tommccallumseo.github.io/glossary/inbound-link">inbound links</a> in order to increase the link profile of their websites and/or get individual content pieces higher in the search results.</p>
                                                                                                                  
<p>There are many different methods and techniques for link building and most marketers and SEOs discover the technique that works best for them through practice. To get you started, here are a few of our favourite guides to link building:</p>

<ol>
 	<li><a href="https://moz.com/beginners-guide-to-link-building">The Beginners Guide to Link Building - Moz</a></li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.quicksprout.com/the-advanced-guide-to-link-building/">The Advanced Guide to Link Building - Quick Sprout</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://pointblankseo.com/link-building-strategies">Link Building Tactics: The Complete List  - Point Blank SEO</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.wordstream.com/link-building">Learn the Fundamentals of Quality Link Building - Wordstream</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://backlinko.com/the-definitive-guide-to-link-building">The Definitive Guide to Link Building - Backlinko</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.hobo-web.co.uk/link-building-strategy-for-beginners-a-month-of-free-tips/">Link Building: How to Build Links to Your Website in 2016 - Hobo Web</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.iacquire.com/resources/link-building-guides/">Noob Guide to Link Building - iAcquire</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://searchengineland.com/guide/seo/link-building-ranking-search-engines">Link Building and Ranking in Search Engines - Search Engine Land</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.matthewwoodward.co.uk/tutorials/the-ultimate-guide-to-tiered-link-building-part-1/">The Ultimate Guide to Tiered Link Building - Matthew Woodward</a></li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.matthewwoodward.co.uk/tutorials/the-ultimate-guide-to-tiered-link-building-part-1/">SEO Link Building Techniques - Red Evolution</a></li>
</ol>

